      "description": "Presenting an exceptional opportunity to acquire a vehicle in truly pristine condition. This specimen has been maintained to an uncompromising standard, reflecting a level of care usually reserved for private collections. From the flawless exterior finish to the factory-fresh interior, every detail confirms its status as a premier investment. We are proud to offer this benchmark-quality vehicle to the discerning driver who demands nothing less than perfection.",
      "price": 48900.0,
